{
  "stem": "1496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the bodies were brought to the cemetery, Jewish cemetery in Krakow Plaszow, and buried in mass grave.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I was the lucky one, because they rounded up some people, and they sent them from the ghetto to this established concentration camp, Krakow Plaszow, on the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I was lucky that they sent me over there to this camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When I arrived in this camp, I was assigned to a machine shop, and I was working in this machine shop.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When you saw the movie and you saw a man making hinges in this shop, I was making handcuffs for the gestapo in the same shop.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was right in the ghetto, and I witnessed the horror of the liquidation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't hide, because what-- before the final liquidation, as I described about the ordering the rest of the people to report in the square, just before then, they rounded up some young people.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- and they sent them to this concentration camp, Krakow Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was one of them, which walked out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, the concentration camp, Krakow Plaszow, was not very far from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So actually, it was in walking distance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was only maybe three, four miles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the main action was only in one day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the main killing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then, it took quite a while, because the Nazis used to walk around, and there were people hiding.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were taking-- taking them from hideouts, and they were executing them right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
